auh prmwqmw Awp hI aus srUp vwlw hY ijs ivc mwieAw dy iqMn guxW dw lyS nhIN huMdw, Awp hI aus srUp vwlw hY ijs ivc mwieAw dy iqMn gux mOjUd hn (Awkwr qoN rihq BI Awp hI hY, qy ieh id`sdw Awkwr rUp BI Awp hI hY)[
